{"tid":280534,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【成功爭取？】蔣麗芸去信行管會 限議員只准添半杯水","createTime":"2017-06-12T07:04:49.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-12T07:31:40.000Z","uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c2c0e6e0bcb9e00c5a697ed1abc4bebe3529fb17","tid":280534,"uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T07:04:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170612/large/1497250676_f185.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170612%2Flarge%2F1497250676_f185.jpg&h=dcc5f080&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n自稱參考多個研究後得知「老鼠嘅天敵係貓」的民建聯立法會議員蔣麗芸，今日再獻新猷。今午她在facebook出post，指立會每次為議員添滿整杯水，惟很多時候有些議員變成「大嘥鬼」，並沒有全部飲完，因此她特意去信立會行管會，建議每次只限添水半杯，「行管會亦從善如流， 回覆稱會提醒管事添水時的份量， 以免浪費！」該帖文配上一幅蔣麗芸和「大嘥鬼」的「合照」，惟蔣的部份似有經修圖痕跡。<br />\n<br />\n有人留言諷刺「好有作為呀個行動，個世界即刻唔同咗」，亦有人建議「進取啲，不准議員在議事廳飲食」。"},{"pid":"178224a0a35be4299f0bd0b1ba3ae610c0d4ed44","tid":280534,"uid":70786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T07:07:59.000Z","msg":"飲唔晒1ml罰1蚊啦on9"},{"pid":"8f21c1b4a00be10e27ee499dc5b99b63c1db9604","tid":280534,"uid":986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T07:09:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>飲唔晒1ml罰1蚊啦on9</blockquote><br />\n1ml一日人工啦"},{"pid":"783673a545f4b73d18ff96580410c39b5bc64b82","tid":280534,"uid":1082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T07:09:58.000Z","msg":"專登p 個樣同大side 鬼一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67e9c26a3694bc74aebb5fa642ec3013d74a9311","tid":280534,"uid":22694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T07:11:18.000Z","msg":"民建聯帶頭啦"},{"pid":"500dd383daf1f8fbed323a5a77b06856f1b79873","tid":280534,"uid":73262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T07:25:45.000Z","msg":"屙半篤尿好無<img src=\"/assets/faces/norma